      <title>Version 2.6.0</title>
      <pubDate>Wed, 22 Jul 2026 10:52:14 +0700</pubDate>
      <sparkle:version>2.6.0</sparkle:version>
      <sparkle:shortVersionString>2.6.0</sparkle:shortVersionString>
      <sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>13.0</sparkle:minimumSystemVersion>
      <description><![CDATA[# StatsBar v2.6.0

Performance and polish.

- **Android (multi-device):** fixed battery health being dropped or misreported when more than one Android phone is connected — each device's state is now tracked independently.
- **CPU:** the frequency readout no longer shows a wrong value for one tick right after reopening the popover.
- **Lower idle usage:** battery power-rail/fan SMC reads and iPhone/iPad USB polling now back off while their panel is closed, cutting background work.
- **UI:** the Android "show more" expand no longer stutters; removed a duplicate "Status" row in the Network panel.

_Not notarized — right-click → Open on first launch (or `xattr -dr com.apple.quarantine /Applications/StatsBar.app`)._]]></description>
